name: You Only Live Twice
description:
You Only Live Twice is a short (puzzle) platformer created in only 48 hours for the GAMEHIGHED Jam 2021.

I strongly recommend downloading because the game requires a fair bit of precision at times and the online player can't always provide that.

Controls:
WASD/Arrow Keys - Move
W/Up/Space - Jump

Credits:
Programming - Me,
Art - Me,
Music - Me,
Everything else - Me
